{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef154be823","title":"北京地质学院红卫兵砸烂修正主义高薪制度联络站战报","origin":"载北京地质学院红卫兵小报《东方红报》第110期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3654c97de1","index":0,"year":1968,"month":1,"day":6,"articleId":"ef154be823"}],"tags":[{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d3d5a5b8c3","type":"title","text":"北京地质学院红卫兵砸烂修正主义高薪制度联络站战报","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"1c0f15f8c7","type":"paragraph","text":"为了彻底结束资产阶级知识分子统治我们学校的现象，为了砸烂修正主义教育路线在经济上的高薪制度，为了彻底打倒我院党内走资派及反动学术权威，从政治上、经济上把他们的威风打下去！我联络站决定，坚决处理我院走资派及反动学术权威的高薪问题，经报请红卫兵总部批准，现决定取消他们的高薪，按下列标准供给生活费：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"017adeca0d","type":"paragraph","text":"1、对于走资派、反动学术权威的生活标准不得超过北京最低生活水平，即12.50元。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"c56ba81bd1","type":"paragraph","text":"2、对其家属、子女应分别对待，他们的生活标准不得超过北京市中等水平18元。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"737034b44e","type":"paragraph","text":"现将处理结果公布如下：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"ac9c7d6942","type":"paragraph","text":"姓  名      原工资      现降到","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"015fde8ca6","type":"paragraph","text":"周守成      170元      12.50元","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"e6c9b569e5","type":"paragraph","text":"聂  克      170元      12.50元","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"93d4681bb1","type":"paragraph","text":"丰  源      170元      12.50元","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"5da0830437","type":"paragraph","text":"冯景兰      345元        31元","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"11be6b8835","type":"paragraph","text":"杨遵义      287元        67元","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"63e696c57a","type":"paragraph","text":"张明哲      207元        49元","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"dd372f5301","type":"paragraph","text":"袁复礼      287元        49元","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"29f21dc169","type":"paragraph","text":"王鸿贞      177元      12.50元","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"39e7d2063b","type":"paragraph","text":" 砸烂修正主义高薪制度联络站一九六八年元月六日","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"86a01ebb07","type":"subtitle","text":"通  令","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"aa5bec75d2","type":"subtitle","text":"（002号）","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"753ad981b2","type":"paragraph","text":"周守成、聂克、丰源、冯景兰、杨遵义、张明哲、袁复礼、王鸿祯于一月九日下午二点三十分至五点到财务科领取生活费。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"},{"id":"9249a80313","type":"paragraph","text":" 砸烂修正主义高薪联络站一九六八年元月九日","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823"}],"page":{"id":"0fbee37bd5","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ef154be823","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}